prompts.frontCover:
An action-packed comic book cover, flat 2D illustration. The scene is a dynamic, split-panel composition with a snowy mountain peak backdrop under a bright blue sky.

In the foreground, Jordan from the photo is illustrated as a superhero, mid-air on a snowboard, kicking up a spray of snow. He is wearing his dark blue t-shirt from the photo, but now with a heroic emblem on the chest that combines a piece of sushi and a wagyu steak. He has a confident, action-hero expression.

Lao Lao from the photo is illustrated as his tech-savvy sidekick, standing at the base of the mountain. She wears her white zip-up jacket from the photo and has a headset on. She's joyfully tossing items up towards Jordan: oversized pieces of sushi, perfectly grilled wagyu steaks, and Chinese takeout boxes that trail steam like rockets. Floating around her are holographic screens displaying lines of glowing green computer code.

The entire scene is framed with bold black outlines and uses a vibrant, high-contrast color palette typical of classic comic books, with Ben-Day dots for shading.

In the center of the sky, inside a classic comic book burst explosion bubble, is the text "Happy Birthday, Jordan!" written in a beautiful, readable, bold handwritten cursive script. The text is colored in a bright yellow with a red outline.
